<li id="cite_note-9"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-9">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation Journal"><a href="Daniel_Chandler" title="Daniel Chandler">Chandler, Daniel</a> (1994). "Who needs suspended inscription?". <i>Computers and Composition</i> <b>11</b> (3): 191–201. <a href="Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/8755-4615(94)90012-4">10.1016/8755-4615(94)90012-4</a>.</span></span></li>
