<li id="cite_note-Rudgley-11"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Rudgley_11-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Rudgley_11-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation book"><a href="Richard_Rudgley" title="Richard Rudgley">Rudgley, Richard</a> (2000). <i>The Lost Civilizations of the Stone Age</i>. New York: Simon &amp; Schuster. pp.&#160;48–57.</span></span></li>
